title: Leave Al Michaels Alone
description:
A colleague apologizes for some bad old tweets (00:01:00). Al Michaels took some heat online for implying Taylor Swift is only popular among teenage girls (00:14:00). The Cullinane family is upset Dave called his cousin a shithead (00:36:00). A live show potential at Matt Roloff's farm? Calls from Rico Bosco & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
